%p== If you have further questions on the COP policy or tools, please contact the COP team at #{mail_to 'cop@unglobalcompact.org'}.

%p We look forward to the timely submission of your complete COP. Once again, please do not hesitate to contact us should you need any assistance. We are more than happy to support you!

%p Sincerely,
%p
  The COP Team
